Perigrafi Dedomenon Waiting time between eruptions and the duration of the eruption for the Old Faithful geyser in Yellowstone National Park, Wyoming, USA. - H stili eruptions: Anaparista ton xrono pou dierkise i ekriksi tou ifestiou - To xaraktiristiko waiting anaparista ton xrono apo tin mia ekriksi mexri tin epomeni.

Zitoumena tis askisis Skopos mas einai na provlepsoume tin diarkia pou tha exei i epomeni ekriksi dedomenou oti tha ginei se 80 lepta.

Fit Linear Regression

  • Arxika kanoume Fit to montelo palindromisis sta dedomena mas
  • Provaloume to summary tou prediction
  • Apo to summary elenxoume an to P-value apo ta F-Statistics einai megalitero to 0.05.
    • Provlima Theloume na elenksoume an uparxei statistiki sisxetisi megaliteri tou 0.05 metaksi ton 2 metavliton
    • Theoroume oti: to error stin linear regression model einai aneksartito tou x kai akolouthei tin tipiki katanomi me zero mean kai statheri diakimansi. Mporoume na apofasisoume an iparxei statistika simantiki sisxetisi metaksi x kai y elenxontas tin mideniki ypothesi oti to = 0.
    • Simperasma Afou to value einai arketa mikrotero apo to 0.05 (p-value: < 2.2e-16), aporiptoume tin mideniki ipothesi oti = 0. Ara iparxei statistika simantiki sisxetisi sto linear regression model.
  • kai stin sinexia provaloume ta dedomena kai tin euthia palindromidid]
fit = lm(eruptions~waiting, data = data)

Provlepsi diarkias ekriksis

Dedomenou oti i ekriksi tha ginei 80 lepta meta tin proigoumeni tis. Na provlepsoume ton xrono pou tha diarkesei

predict(fit, data.frame(waiting=80))
##       1 
## 4.17622

Kataskeuazoume 95% diastima empistosinis gia to eruption dedomenou oti o xronos anamonis einai 80 min

  • filter dataset na kratisoume mono tis paratirisis me anamoni 80 min
  • ypologismos mesou, size
  • ypologismos diastimatos empistosisnis
  • Upologismos diastimatos empistosis [L,U] gia ton meso:
# filter 80 min waiting dataset
data_80min = data[data$waiting == 80,]
data_80min

Upologizoume to 95% diastima empistosinis gia tin metavliti eruptions

Gia tin evresi tou Diastimatos empistosinis tha xrisimopoieisoume tin protasi 15.8.4 tou vivliou Theoria pithantitwn kai stoixeia statistikis Analisis selida 874

x0 = 80
confidence = 0.95
my_data = data$eruptions
mean = mean(data$waiting)
size = length(my_data)
y_hat = predict(fit, data.frame(waiting=x0))
zscore = qnorm(0.025,lower.tail=FALSE)

sse <- sum((fitted(fit) - my_data)^2)
S = sqrt(sse/(size - 2))
S_xx = sum(my_data^2) - (size*(mean^2))
S_y = S*(sqrt(1 + (1/size) + ((x0 - mean)^2)/S_xx))

L = y_hat - (S_y*zscore)
U = y_hat + (S_y*zscore)

message("The lower bound is: ",round(L,4))
## The lower bound is: 3.2013
message("The upper bound is: ",round(U,4))
## The upper bound is: 5.1511

Kataskeuaste diastima empistosinis 95% gia tin provlepsi tis metavlitis eruption

Auto to pernoume kanontas xrisimopoiontas tin methodo confinit() gia to filtrarismeno sinio dedomenon pou periexei mono tis paratirisis me waiting time 80min kai ekpedeuontas ena kenourio linear regression model me auto to Dataset.

Symperasmata Paratiroume oti to diastima empistosisnis gia ta dedomena kai gia tin provlepsei einai to idio gia to dataset pou perieixe mono ta dedomena me waiting 80 min (4.152208 4.776792)

## Diagramma ipolipwn Gramikis palindromisis.

  • Arxika ipologizoume ta residuals tis gramikis palindromisis ws pros ton xrono.
  • Provaloume to Q-Q plot.
  • Sti sinexeia plotaroume to histogram gia 20 buckets
Residual = resid(fit) 
Fitted = fitted(fit)
plot(Fitted,Residual, 
     main="Old Faithful geyser dataset: Fitted vs. Residuals", 
     xlab="Fitted Waiting Time (minutes)")
abline(h=0, col="blue")

qqnorm(Residual)
qqline(Residual, col="red")

Residual = resid(fit) 
hist(Residual, main = "Histogram of Residuals - 20 breaks", ylab = "Density", 
     ylim = c(0, 1.5),
     prob = TRUE,breaks=20, col="lightblue")
curve(dnorm(x, mean = mean(Residual), sd = sd(Residual)), col="red", add=TRUE)
